"title": "5661: brothers",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5661",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The son of one's parents, or of either mother or father. God's people may be referred to collectively as brothers, all being children of one heavenly Father.</p>\n<h2>Close relationship between brothers</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev21:1-Lev21:3\">LEV 21:1–21:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num6:6-Num6:7\">NUM 6:6–6:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:54\">DEU 28:54</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov18:24\">PRO 18:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek44:25\">EZK 44:25</a></p>\n<h2>Duties of brothers</h2>\n<h3>Levirate marriage</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut25:5-Deut25:10\">DEU 25:5–25:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen38:6-Gen38:11\">GEN 38:6–38:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt22:23-Matt22:30\">MAT 22:23–22:30</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:18-Mark12:25\">MRK 12:18–12:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke20:27-Luke20:36\">LUK 20:27–20:36</a></p>\n<h3>Participation in arrangement of marriages for sisters</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen34:11-Gen34:17\">GEN 34:11–34:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen24:50-Gen24:60\">GEN 24:50–24:60</a></p>\n<h3>Protection of sisters</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam13:1-2Sam13:33\">2SA 13:1–13:33</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen34:24-Gen34:31\">GEN 34:24–34:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev21:3\">LEV 21:3</a></p>\n<h3>Younger brothers taking news of older brothers to their father</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam17:17-1Sam17:18\">1SA 17:17–17:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen37:12-Gen37:17\">GEN 37:12–37:17</a></p>\n<h2>The priority of the eldest brother</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut21:15-Deut21:17\">DEU 21:15–21:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen43:33\">GEN 43:33</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen44:12\">GEN 44:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam20:29\">1SA 20:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr5:1-1Chr5:2\">1CH 5:1–5:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr21:1-2Chr21:3\">2CH 21:1–21:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps89:27\">PSA 89:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:16\">HEB 12:16</a></p>\n<h2>Examples of younger brothers superseding their elder brothers</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen25:21-Gen25:23\">GEN 25:21–25:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen48:8-Gen48:20\">GEN 48:8–48:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut33:13-Deut33:17\">DEU 33:13–33:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam16:6-1Sam16:13\">1SA 16:6–16:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs2:22\">1KI 2:22</a></p>\n<h2>Brothers as heirs</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num27:8-Num27:11\">NUM 27:8–27:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl4:8\">ECC 4:8</a></p>\n<h2>Twin brothers</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen25:24-Gen25:26\">GEN 25:24–25:26</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen38:27-Gen38:30\">GEN 38:27–38:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal1:2-Mal1:3\">MAL 1:2–1:3</a></p>\n<h2>Half-brothers</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg11:1-Judg11:2\">JDG 11:1–11:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen21:8-Gen21:9\">GEN 21:8–21:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg8:30-Judg8:31\">JDG 8:30–8:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg9:1-Judg9:6\">JDG 9:1–9:6</a></p>\n<h2>Brothers-in-law</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num10:29-Num10:32\">NUM 10:29–10:32</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen38:8\">GEN 38:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut25:5\">DEU 25:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut25:7\">DEU 25:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg4:11\">JDG 4:11</a></p>\n<h2>Examples of brothers failing to live up to expectations of them</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen4:8-Gen4:12\">GEN 4:8–4:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen37:3-Gen37:4\">GEN 37:3–37:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen37:12-Gen37:33\">GEN 37:12–37:33</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen38:6-Gen38:10\">GEN 38:6–38:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg9:1-Judg9:5\">JDG 9:1–9:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr21:4\">2CH 21:4</a></p>\n<h2>Application of the term ``brothers''</h2>\n<h3>To siblings</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen42:32\">GEN 42:32</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen16:9-Gen16:12\">GEN 16:9–16:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen25:18\">GEN 25:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg16:31\">JDG 16:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam17:17-1Sam17:22\">1SA 17:17–17:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam22:1\">1SA 22:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr21:13\">2CH 21:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh1:2\">NEH 1:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh5:14\">NEH 5:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job19:17\">JOB 19:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job42:11\">JOB 42:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov17:17\">PRO 17:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt10:21\">MAT 10:21</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark13:12\">MRK 13:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke21:16\">LUK 21:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:55\">MAT 13:55</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark6:3\">MRK 6:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John7:3-John7:5\">JHN 7:3–7:5</a></p>\n<h3>To relatives</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ruth4:3\">RUT 4:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num36:2\">NUM 36:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov27:10\">PRO 27:10</a></p>\n<h3>To members of the same tribe</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam19:11-2Sam19:12\">2SA 19:11–19:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num8:26\">NUM 8:26</a></p>\n<h3>To Israelites</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut3:18\">DEU 3:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut10:9\">DEU 10:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut17:15\">DEU 17:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg20:23\">JDG 20:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam19:41\">2SA 19:41</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr13:2\">1CH 13:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer7:15\">JER 7:15</a></p>\n<h3>To descendants of a common ancestor</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num20:14\">NUM 20:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut2:4\">DEU 2:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut23:7\">DEU 23:7</a></p>\n<h3>To equals and fellow-citizens</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev19:17\">LEV 19:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut1:16\">DEU 1:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut15:3\">DEU 15:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut22:1\">DEU 22:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut23:19\">DEU 23:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam2:26\">2SA 2:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:22-Matt5:24\">MAT 5:22–5:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt7:3-Matt7:5\">MAT 7:3–7:5</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:41-Luke6:42\">LUK 6:41–6:42</a></p>\n<h2>Love for God must exceed love for brothers</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke14:26\">LUK 14:26</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut33:9\">DEU 33:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt19:29\">MAT 19:29</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:29-Mark10:30\">MRK 10:29–10:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:29-Luke18:30\">LUK 18:29–18:30</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ calls his disciples his ``brothers''</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:49-Matt12:50\">MAT 12:49–12:50</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark3:34-Mark3:35\">MRK 3:34–3:35</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:21\">LUK 8:21</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:34-Matt25:40\">MAT 25:34–25:40</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt28:10\">MAT 28:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John20:17\">JHN 20:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb2:11\">HEB 2:11</a></p>\n<h2>The fraternal relationship among God's people</h2>\n<h3>Fellow Christians called brothers</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt23:8\">MAT 23:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts15:23\">ACT 15:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts28:14\">ACT 28:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor5:11\">1CO 5:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor1:1\">2CO 1:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor9:3\">2CO 9:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor11:9\">2CO 11:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor12:18\">2CO 12:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess2:13\">2TH 2:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phlm1:1\">PHM 1:1</a></p>\n<h3>Believers urged to love each other</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess4:10\">1TH 4:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:10\">ROM 12:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas2:14-Jas2:17\">JAS 2:14–2:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:17\">1PE 2:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet1:5-2Pet1:9\">2PE 1:5–1:9</a></p>\n<h3>The church referred to as ``the brothers''</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts14:2\">ACT 14:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:30\">ACT 9:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts11:1\">ACT 11:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts11:29\">ACT 11:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts15:3\">ACT 15:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts16:2\">ACT 16:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts17:14\">ACT 17:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts21:17\">ACT 21:17</a></p>\n<h2>Brother as an honorific term</h2>\n<h3>Equals called ``brothers''</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen29:4\">GEN 29:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam30:22-1Sam30:23\">1SA 30:22–30:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam1:26\">2SA 1:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam20:9\">2SA 20:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs13:29-1Kgs13:30\">1KI 13:29–13:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts1:16\">ACT 1:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:37\">ACT 2:37</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts3:17\">ACT 3:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts7:2\">ACT 7:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts22:1\">ACT 22:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts28:17\">ACT 28:17</a></p>\n<h3>Fellow Christians called ``brothers''</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:10\">1CO 1:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:17\">ACT 9:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts22:13\">ACT 22:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:12\">ROM 8:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom11:25\">ROM 11:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor2:1\">1CO 2:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor7:24\">1CO 7:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor8:1\">2CO 8:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal4:31\">GAL 4:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess2:14\">1TH 2:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb3:1\">HEB 3:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:16\">JAS 1:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas5:10\">JAS 5:10</a></p>",
